"729d31b7789ba3426ee52621350b6b7f59cf28af","tid":2032603,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"好撚多人買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879973ac316a732ea61fb3576dd7ee2f2fc19a3b","tid":2032603,"uid":215876,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"黑狗就係唔想比人數聚到<br />\n先一早射tg<br />\n然後係連登係咁吹風叫轉場<br />\n<br />\n今日有人數集合抗國安法嘅畫面<br />\n支共個國安騙局就無得講"},{"pid":"94d1bb6b41ce38edf89e624b8ffcdb131f617a5b","tid":2032603,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf50d0f2b6dfe90830230996ab4f92f35115eca","tid":2032603,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445a1811e7e536d3ee48661a0771d8f8cdc4f359","tid":2032603,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c88c01ac7d268978a72caf6f0b01bc6b7b2f373","tid":2032603,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"五毛咁努力，證明人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e054db9c5772ecf52ee66a3f816f1b523c3d6dc3","tid":2032603,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"說明支那真係好驚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=3b6c2dd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"e469b2d1efef0f4f58e10664a2063d8c941e9cdc","tid":2032603,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"失敗撚不願面對"},{"pid":"566d99b666e224e2128095cb319fef159311e3fd","tid":2032603,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"五毛失敗撚仲有乜野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\"